name: Basic Grid CSS Framework
body:
### Basic Grid CSS Framework
My first project on github, just a basic css grid framework to easily layout out websites with css.
Feel free to use it in your projects.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Basic Grid? [Contact support](mailto:hellodave.sq@gmail.com) and I'll help you sort it out.
